  <brief_title>Pilot Study: Intraoperative Clonidine and Postoperative Behaviour</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomised Controlled Pilot Study: Does Intraoperative Clonidine Reduce the Incidence of Post-hospitalisation Negative Behaviour Changes in Children Who Are Distressed During the Induction of General Anaesthesia?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
